# OpInterface definitions
## DotInterface (`DotInterface`)

Base interface for Dot graph generation
### Methods:
#### `getNodeColor`

```c++
vpux::DotNodeColor getNodeColor();
```
Get node color
NOTE: This method *must* be implemented by the user.

#### `printAttributes`

```c++
bool printAttributes(llvm::raw_ostream&os);
```
If non empty overrides the default attributes in the dot graph
NOTE: This method *must* be implemented by the user.

An extended version of view-like operation.
It allows to define several resulting views in single operation.

### Methods:
#### `getViewSource`

```c++

```
